<% content_for :title do %>
  <%= "Papoters | Be advisor" %>
<% end %>

<div class="home" style='background-image: url("<%= image_path('backgrounds/background_advisor.png') %>");'>

  <div class="home-banner text-center bg-gray-transparent">
    <div class="home-banner-top home-content-wrapper">
      <div class="home-flex-800">
        <h1>Your knowledge and your experience have value!</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-banner-middle home-content-wrapper bg-green-transparent">
      <div class="home-flex-600">
        <%= link_to "Publish an offer as advisor",new_offer_path, id: "home-give-advice-link" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-banner-bottom home-content-wrapper">
      <%= link_to root_path, id: "home-arrow-down" do %>
        <p class="no-margin-bottom">Find out more</p>
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="home-inspirations-top bg-gray-transparent"></div>
    <div id="home-inspirations-animated-background" class="bg-white" style='background-image: url("<%= image_path('backgrounds/background_line.png') %>");'>
      <div class="home-inspirations-body-2 text-center padded-top-l home-content-wrapper" style='background-image: url("<%= image_path('backgrounds/background_disclose_line.png') %>");'>
        <div class="home-flex-700">
          <h2 class="white">Everybody's got some special knowledge.<br>What is yours?</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style='background-image: url("<%= image_path('backgrounds/background_grid_gray.png') %>");' class="padded-top-l padded-bottom-xl text-center bg-white">
    <div class="home-content-wrapper padded-bottom-l">
      <div class="home-flex-700">
        <h2>Advise people, build your reputation and make yourself valuable.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 padded-bottom-m">
          <div class="home-guideline-container text-center">
            <%= image_tag 'guidelines/publish_offer.svg' %>
            <div class="home-guideline-text text-left">
              <p>You are probably recognize for your special knowledge. got some knowledge that many people would be happy to learn from. Papoters give you the tools to do it right.</p>
              <p>Type your search on Papoters and find out which advisor offers something that matches your needs.</p>
              <i class="fa fa-info-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4>1 &nbsp;-&nbsp; Publish an offer</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 padded-bottom-m">
          <div class="home-guideline-container text-center">
            <%= image_tag 'guidelines/answer_requests.svg' %>
            <div class="home-guideline-text text-left">
              <p>Get in touch with your advisor and detail your needs. This starts a private session between you and your advisor.</p>
              <p>Your three first sessions are for free..</p>
              <i class="fa fa-info-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4>2 &nbsp;-&nbsp; Answer to requests</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 padded-bottom-m">
          <div class="home-guideline-container text-center">
            <%= image_tag 'guidelines/deliver_advice.svg' %>
            <div class="home-guideline-text text-left">
              <p>Once the session is open, your advisor is dedicated to answering your needs as part of your agreement.</p>
              <p>The means of communication depend on what you agreed in the proposition: messaging, phone call, visio call, meeting, etc.</p>
              <i class="fa fa-info-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4>3 &nbsp;-&nbsp; Deliver advice</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 padded-bottom-m">
          <div class="home-guideline-container text-center">
            <%= image_tag 'guidelines/get_rewards.svg' %>
            <div class="home-guideline-text text-left">
              <p>The session can be closed after the deadline set in the proposition has passed.</p>
              <p>Evaluate your session and leave a review to your advisor, based on whether or not the sesssion's targets were achieved.</p>
              <i class="fa fa-info-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4>4 &nbsp;-&nbsp; Get your rewards !</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="padded-top-xs">
      <%= link_to "Publish an offer", new_offer_path, class: "btn btn-green home-btn" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style='background-image: url("<%= image_path('backgrounds/background.png') %>");' class="bg-white">
    <div class="padded-top-l padded-bottom-xl text-center bg-gray-transparent">
      <div class="padded-bottom-m home-content-wrapper">
        <div class="home-flex-700">
          <h2 class="font-weight-normal">Papoters' community is growing!</h2>
          <h3 class="font-weight-normal">Get inspired by what people already offer.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="padded-top-xs">
        <button id="home-btn-search-trigger" class="btn btn btn-yellow home-btn">
          Find an advisor &nbsp;&nbsp;<i class='fa fa-search'></i>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
